From: Jan Martens <44572196+JanMa@users.noreply.github.com>
Date: Tue, 17 Mar 2026 21:37:58 +0100
Subject: [PATCH 17/22] UI: Upgrade EmberJS to 4.12 LTS (#2653)

* v4.4.0...v4.8.1

ember-data upgrade to 4.7 outstanding

Signed-off-by: Jan Martens <jan@martens.eu.org>

* define strict ember-data model relationships

Signed-off-by: Jan Martens <jan@martens.eu.org>

* update ember-data to 4.7

Signed-off-by: Jan Martens <jan@martens.eu.org>

* v4.8.1...v4.12.3

Signed-off-by: Jan Martens <jan@martens.eu.org>

* fix cleanupModel to prevent destroy after unloadRecord

Remove model.destroy() calls after removeRecord() in controller
cleanupModel methods. The removeRecord utility already unloads the
record from the store, so calling destroy() on an unloaded record
causes 'Assertion Failed: <model> is not a record instantiated by
@ember-data/store' errors during route transitions.

Signed-off-by: Jan Martens <jan@martens.eu.org>

* Fix expected stable identifier errors

Signed-off-by: Jan Martens <jan@martens.eu.org>

* stub window.confirm in tests

Signed-off-by: Jan Martens <jan@martens.eu.org>

* fix undefined changedAttributes error

Signed-off-by: Jan Martens <jan@martens.eu.org>

* fix uncaought handler in pretender issue

Forward all undhandled paths

Signed-off-by: Jan Martens <jan@martens.eu.org>

* update code-mirror to ember-modifiers v4 API

Signed-off-by: Jan Martens <jan@martens.eu.org>

* fix more undefined errors

Signed-off-by: Jan Martens <jan@martens.eu.org>

* fix oidc test failures

Signed-off-by: Jan Martens <jan@martens.eu.org>

* fix auth-methods list test

Signed-off-by: Jan Martens <jan@martens.eu.org>

* fix MFA test errors

Signed-off-by: Jan Martens <jan@martens.eu.org>

* fix timing issue in tests

Ensure we wait until the login or logout page has fully loaded

Signed-off-by: Jan Martens <jan@martens.eu.org>

* switch back to npm-run-all

concurrently was causing some issues

Signed-off-by: Jan Martens <jan@martens.eu.org>

* fix template-lint errors

Signed-off-by: Jan Martens <jan@martens.eu.org>

* fix yarn.lock

It was corrupted during rebase

Signed-off-by: Jan Martens <jan@martens.eu.org>

* add changelog

Signed-off-by: Jan Martens <jan@martens.eu.org>

